```
@easyemachine verilator_fixes % /opt/verilator.20250910/bin/verilator --version
Verilator 5.041 devel rev v5.040-85-g5349b51e7
```

What OS and distribution are you using?

```
@easyemachine verilator_fixes % uname -a
Darwin easyemachine.local 24.6.0 Darwin Kernel Version 24.6.0: Mon Jul 14 11:30:40 PDT 2025; root:xnu-11417.140.69~1/RELEASE_ARM64_T6041 arm64
```

Thanks,
